Titolo: NCAA Football 2002

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: NCAA Football 2002 is a video game of the sports genre released in 2001 by Tiburon. The cover athlete is the 2001 Heisman winning Florida State quarterback Chris Weinke. The game featured all (as of 2001) Division 1-A schools along with all SWAC, MEAC, and Ivy League schools. This game notably did not have a Create-a-School option, and is the only game to feature the EA Sports fight song as the main menu music.

